[MQ3 Alcohol Sensor]
VCC   → 5V
GND   → GND
AOUT  → A0

[SIM800 GSM Module]
TX    → D3
RX    → D2
VCC   → 3.3V
GND   → GND

[NEO-6M GPS Module]
TX    → D9 (AltSoftSerial RX)
RX    → D8 (optional)
VCC   → 5V
GND   → GND

[Accelerometer]
X OUT → A1
Y OUT → A2
Z OUT → A3
VCC   → 3.3V
GND   → GND

[LEDs / Vibration]
D6    → Status LED
D10   → v1 Output
D11   → v2 Output
D12   → v3 Output
